  TITLE     Monoterpenes in the glandular trichomes of tomato are synthesized from a neryl diphosphate precursor rather than geranyl diphosphate.
  JOURNAL   Proc. Natl. Acad. Sci. U. S. A. 106 (2009) 10865-70.
  ORGANISM  Solanum lycopersicum
